name: Cupipanda (Prototype)
description:
You are Cupipanda. You must save the Pandas before they become extinct!

This is a prototype we developed of a casual game. The idea is that the full game will include a lot more levels, and interesting mechanics.

If you have any questions or feedback feel free to send an e-mail to: ido.markowicz@gmail.com

Thank you, and have fun playing
